    <h2>
        About Andrew Comeau and AndrewComeau.com</h2>
    <p>
        AndrewComeau.com is a site dedicated to the sharing of programming knowledge 
        with those looking for solutions or interested in learning more about 
        programming technologies and the software development field.</p>
    <p>
        This site will include articles that examine the professional as well as the 
        technical aspects of software development.&nbsp; While featuring professional, 
        quality articles on a diverse set of programming technologies, the site will 
        also offer content that examines the educational and professional realities of 
        working in the programming field.</p>
    <p>
        AndrewComeau.com is being developed with Microsoft Visual Studio 2010 
        Professional and ASP.NET 4.0.</p>
