    learning how to design database systems, first with
    <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paradox_(database)" 
        style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" target="_blank">Borland Paradox</a><span 
        class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and then<span 
        class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a 
